00:55:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australian-pm-albanese-says-china-military-air-incident-unacceptable-2024-05-07/</guid></item><item><title>以色列袭击加沙后油价小幅上涨，而停战谈判仍在继续</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-edges-up-after-israel-strikes-gaza-while-truce-talks-continue-2024-05-07/</link><description>以色列袭击加沙的拉法后，周二早些时候油价上涨，而与哈马斯的停火谈判仍在继续，但没有解决。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 00:40:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/oil-edges-up-after-israel-strikes-gaza-while-truce-talks-continue-2024-05-07/</guid></item><item><title>法国马克龙感谢中国习近平在干邑问题上的“开放态度”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/frances-macron-thanks-chinas-xi-his-open-attitude-cognac-issue-2024-05-06/</link><description>法国总统马克龙周一感谢中国国家主席习近平在干邑白兰地反倾销调查中所表现出的“开放态度”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 23:21:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/frances-macron-thanks-chinas-xi-his-open-attitude-cognac-issue-2024-05-06/</guid></item><item><title>法国和中国公司在习近平巴黎之行期间签署协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/french-chinese-firms-ink-deals-sidelines-xis-paris-visit-2024-05-06/</link><description>周一，在中国国家主席习近平访问法国首都期间，法国和中国企业签署了能源、金融和运输等领域的协议。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 16:32:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/french-chinese-firms-ink-deals-sidelines-xis-paris-visit-2024-05-06/</guid></item><item><title>蔚来高管表示，蔚来有望于五月推出首款大众市场汽车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/nio-track-unveil-its-first-mass-market-car-may-executive-says-2024-05-06/</link><description>周一，中国高端电动汽车制造商蔚来汽车的一位高管告诉路透社，蔚来汽车有望在本月底之前以大众市场品牌推出一款新车型，并于明年在欧洲推出第二款小型电动汽车，售价将低于 3 万美元。 。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 15:09:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/nio-track-unveil-its-first-mass-market-car-may-executive-says-2024-05-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国习近平支持马克龙呼吁全球奥运休战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/macron-von-der-leyen-urge-china-press-russia-over-ukraine-2024-05-06/</link><description>在法国总统和欧盟委员会主席敦促他利用对俄罗斯的影响力结束乌克兰战争后，中国国家主席习近平周一呼吁在今年夏天巴黎奥运会期间实现全球休战。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 15:00:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/macron-von-der-leyen-urge-china-press-russia-over-ukraine-2024-05-06/</guid></item><item><title>澳大利亚谴责中国“不安全”空中对抗</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-criticizes-china-over-unsafe-aerial-confrontation-over-yellow-sea-2024-05-06/</link><description>澳大利亚周一表示，在黄海上空的一场“不安全”和“不可接受”的对抗中，一架中国战斗机危及一架澳大利亚军用直升机。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 11:40:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-criticizes-china-over-unsafe-aerial-confrontation-over-yellow-sea-2024-05-06/</guid></item><item><title>沃伦·巴菲特的粉丝为他离开后制定了自己的路线</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/warren-buffetts-fans-plot-their-own-course-when-he-leaves-2024-05-06/</link><description>93岁的伯克希尔哈撒韦公司首席执行官、亿万富翁沃伦·巴菲特在思考自己的未来时，周六告诉股东，如果幸运的话，他还能再活六七年，但他补充说，“这可能明天就结束了”。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 10:02:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/warren-buffetts-fans-plot-their-own-course-when-he-leaves-2024-05-06/</guid></item><item><title>法国财政部长表示欢迎中国电动汽车制造商比亚迪在法国开设工厂</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-maker-byd-welcome-open-factory-france-french-finance-minister-says-2024-05-06/</link><description>财政部长布鲁诺·勒梅尔周一表示，如果中国电动汽车巨头比亚迪决定在法国开设工厂，法国将欢迎该公司。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 09:45:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-maker-byd-welcome-open-factory-france-french-finance-minister-says-2024-05-06/</guid></item><item><title>五一假期期间中国房屋销售量较 2023 年下降 47%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-home-sales-slump-47-over-may-day-holiday-vs-2023-2024-05-06/</link><description>周一的一项私人调查显示，“五一”公共假期期间，中国的日均房屋销售量同比下降 47%，较 2019 年同一假期期间大流行前的水平下降约 30%。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 08:48:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-home-sales-slump-47-over-may-day-holiday-vs-2023-2024-05-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国五一假期消费在新冠疫情后的复苏中喜忧参半</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-may-day-holiday-spending-delivers-mixed-picture-post-covid-recovery-2024-05-06/</link><description>政府周一公布的数据显示，在中国最长的假期之一“五一”假期期间，国内游客的支出为 1669 亿元人民币（合 231.3 亿美元），比疫情前的水平增长 13.5%，但人均支出落后于 2019 年的水平。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 08:16:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-may-day-holiday-spending-delivers-mixed-picture-post-covid-recovery-2024-05-06/</guid></item><item><title>中国卫生机构在代孕索赔后对医院进行调查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-health-body-probes-hospital-after-surrogacy-claims-2024-05-06/</link><description>中国国家卫生健康委员会表示，正在对西南特大城市重庆的一家医院涉嫌参与代孕进行调查，该问题在社交媒体上广泛传播，这在中国是非法的。</description><pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 07:47:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinas-health-body-probes-hospital-after-surrogacy-claims-2024-05-06/</guid></item></channel></rss>